{"id": "art-1366", "label": "Art. 1366", "title": "Art. 1366: Răspunderea minorului şi a persoanei care beneficiază de consiliere judiciară sau tutelă specială", "slug": "art-1366", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1199268840\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1111\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1199268840\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 1366:\nR&#259;spunderea minorului &#351;i a persoanei care beneficiaz&#259; de\nconsiliere judiciar&#259; sau tutel&#259; special&#259; </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_233854961\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1110\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_233854961\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Minorul care nu a împlinit vârsta de 14 ani sau persoana\ncare beneficiaz&#259; de tutela special&#259; nu r&#259;spunde de prejudiciul\ncauzat, dac&#259; nu se dovede&#351;te discern&#259;mântul s&#259;u la data\ns&#259;vâr&#351;irii faptei.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1941703124\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1109\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1941703124\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Minorul care a împlinit vârsta de 14 ani r&#259;spunde\nde prejudiciul cauzat, în afar&#259; de cazul în care dovede&#351;te c&#259; a\nfost lipsit de discern&#259;mânt la data s&#259;vâr&#351;irii faptei.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_330994881\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1108\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_330994881\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Dispozi&#355;iile alin. (1) sunt aplicabile &#351;i\npersoanei care beneficiaz&#259; de tutel&#259; special&#259;, iar prevederile\nalin. (2) &#351;i persoanei care beneficiaz&#259; de consiliere judiciar&#259;.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}